transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Thank you for calling Viagra, how can I help you?

Speaker 2: Hi, my name is Bartolomeo Grillo and I've been calling you because I wanted to cancel my school subscription.

Speaker 1: Could you please help me with the same?

Speaker 2: Yeah, can I have your phone number so I can pull up your account?

Speaker 1: Yes, it's 617-866-2995.

Speaker 2: All right, thank you.

Speaker 1: Bart, can you just confirm your date of birth?

Speaker 2: The date of birth is December 21, 1998.

Speaker 1: No, that's not the right date, no.

Speaker 2: I know you're a third party and due to HIPAA regulations, I can't talk to you, so I need you to have your client call us directly because due to HIPAA, I cannot give you any information because it's medical records.

Speaker 1: So you have to have your client call in directly.

Speaker 2: Got it, no worries.

Speaker 1: Thank you so much for your time.

Speaker 2: No problem, have a good one.

Speaker 1: Thank you, bye.
